OL,3,CTrial begins for man charged with 15
OL,4,Ccounts of sexual offences
OL,6,FA 44-year-old man has appeared at
OL,7,FJersey's Royal Court for the first day
OL,8,Fof a five-day trial (Monday 10 March
OL,9,F2025).
OL,11,FDean James Plowman has been charged
OL,12,Fwith 15 counts of sexual offences
OL,13,Fagainst a child.
OL,15,FThese include seven counts of rape and
OL,16,Ffive counts of sexual penetration
OL,17,Fwithout consent.
OL,19,FPlowman has also been charged with two
OL,20,Fcounts of grave and criminal assault
OL,21,Fagainst the same child.
