OL,3,CTrial begins for man charged with 15
OL,4,Ccounts of sexual offences
OL,6,FAll of the offences are alleged to
OL,7,Fhave taken place between February 2019
OL,8,Fand January 2023.
OL,10,FOpening for the prosecution, Crown
OL,11,FAdvocate Simon Thomas described the
OL,12,Fcase as "serious and prolonged sexual
OL,13,Fabuse".
OL,15,FThe jury spent most of the day
OL,16,Fwatching video-recorded evidence with
OL,17,Fthe complainant.
OL,19,FIn it, the complainant described what
OL,20,Fshe claims happened to her and how, at
OL,21,Ftimes, she was in pain.
